&lt;h2 id=&quot;luis-ricardo-martinez-diaz&quot;&gt;&lt;center&gt;Luis Ricardo Martínez Díaz&lt;&#x2F;center&gt;&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;hr &#x2F;&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;E-mail: &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:info@luis-ti.dev.br&quot;&gt;info@luis-ti.dev.br&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;. | Celular: &lt;a href=&quot;tel:+5511933014430&quot;&gt;5511933014430&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;. | Github: &lt;a rel=&quot;noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;github.com&#x2F;m00sp&quot;&gt;m00sp&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;. | Localização: Vila Matilde, SP, Brasil. &lt;&#x2F;br&gt; Site: &lt;a rel=&quot;noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.luis-ti.dev.br&quot;&gt;www.luis-ti.dev.br&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
